title: water damaged board solved thank you
message: I just fix today a core 2 duo board that I don't remember the model was like a 2009 , but I got cash out of it , I replace like 21 components , 2 mosfets , randoms resistors and caps around u7000 and 3.4v inductor  and resistors  between others, I also a trace a wire because corroded paths , I didn't get like a lot of money but something is something , thank you for this forum , I hope you guys never re think and close it , because having the privilege to get answers here is amazing.
